fields.physical_description:
Each item or set has a small white round label. These were placed on the parts at Palitoy where they were tested. The smaller items are contained in plastic bags; on which the label has been placed.
*Imperial Attack Base sections 
1. Code No. D3432; side wall shaped as an iceberg, white injection moulded plastic 
2,3. Code No. D3433 and D3434; blocks shaped as icebergs, white injection moulded plastic
4. Code No. D3435; open rectangle with pair of long legs on one edge, grey injection moulded plastic
5-9. Code No. D3436 - D3439; marked IA BASE; 
        D3436 and D3437 land mine levers; D3438 snow bank lever; and                                                                                                                                                                          
        D3439 ice bridge lever, white injection moulded plastic 
10-16. Code No. D3440; IA Base; containing 6 lever covers, white injection moulded plastic. Dated 23.6.81 
17-23. Code No. D3441; IA Base; containing 6 monitors, black injection moulded plastic. Dated 23.6.81 
24-30. Code No. D3442; IA Base; containing 6 laser cannons, black injection moulded plastic. Dated 23.6.81 
31. Code No. D3443 IA Base; containing 6 (very small) Mylar Clickers, opaque injection moulded plastic. Dated 23.6.81 
32-41. Code No. D3449; containing 4 different round discs and 9 mechanical arms, grey injection moulded plastic 

*Turret and Probot Playset 
42. Code No. D3454; turret top half, cream injection moulded plastic 
43. Code No. D3455; turret bottom half, cream injection moulded plastic 44. Code No. D3456; turret cap, cream injection moulded plastic
45. Code No. D3457; turret support stick, white injection moulded plastic 46. Code No. D3458; turret cone, cream injection moulded plastic 
47. Code No. D3459; cone door, cream injection moulded plastic 
48. Code No. D3461; 3 very small strips of opaque plastic 
49. Code No. D3463; ice cap lever, white injection moulded plastic 
50. Code No. D3464; lever mechanism, white injection moulded plastic 51. Code No. D3465; laser cannon, black injection moulded plastic 
52. Code No. D3466; lever mechanism, opaque plastic 
53. Code No. D3467; triangular lever mechanism, opaque plastic
fields.title: Imperial Attack Base and Turret & Probot Playsets
